<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>구매 완료 - PharmChecker</title>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .container {
        background-color: white;
        max-width: 600px;
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 16px;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #27ae60;
        color: white;
        padding: 40px 30px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .header h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .header p {
        font-size: 16px;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }
      .checkmark {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        margin: 0 auto 20px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 48px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 40px 30px;
      }
      .info-section {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }
      .info-section h2 {
        font-size: 18px;
        color: #2c3e50;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #ecf0f1;
      }
      .info-item {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 12px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #f8f9fa;
      }
      .info-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }
      .info-label {
        color: #7f8c8d;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .info-value {
        color: #2c3e50;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 14px;
        text-align: right;
      }
      .amount-highlight {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .amount-highlight .label {
        color: #7f8c8d;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      .amount-highlight .value {
        color: #27ae60;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .button-group {
        margin-top: 30px;
        display: flex;
        gap: 10px;
      }
      .button {
        flex: 1;
        padding: 16px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .button-primary {
        background-color: #667eea;
        color: white;
      }
      .button-primary:hover {
        background-color: #5568d3;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
      }
      .button-secondary {
        background-color: #ecf0f1;
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      .button-secondary:hover {
        background-color: #dfe6e9;
      }
      .notice {
        background-color: #fff3cd;
        border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
        padding: 15px;
        margin-top: 30px;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }
      .notice p {
        color: #856404;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="checkmark">✓</div>
        <h1>구매가 완료되었습니다!</h1>
        <p>PharmChecker 구독이 활성화되었습니다</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="content">
        <div class="info-section">
          <h2>구매 정보</h2>
          <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">이메일</span>
            <span class="info-value" id="email">-</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">구독 플랜</span>
            <span class="info-value" id="plan">-</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">상품명</span>
            <span class="info-value" id="orderName">-</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-section">
          <h2>결제 상세</h2>
          <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">주문번호</span>
            <span class="info-value" id="orderId">-</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <span class="info-label">결제 키</span>
            <span class="info-value" id="paymentKey" style="font-size: 11px; word-break: break-all;">-</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="amount-highlight">
          <div class="label">결제 금액</div>
          <div class="value" id="amount">0원</div>
        </div>

        <div class="notice">
          <p>
            ✓ 구매하신 플랜은 즉시 사용 가능합니다.<br>
            ✓ 구독 관련 안내 메일이 발송되었습니다.<br>
            ✓ 문의사항은 고객센터를 이용해주세요.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="button-group">
          <button class="button button-secondary" onclick="window.location.href='/pharmchecker'">
            메인으로
          </button>
          <button class="button button-primary" onclick="alert('서비스 준비 중입니다.')">
            서비스 시작하기
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script>
      // URL 파라미터에서 정보 가져오기
      const urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
      
      const email = urlParams.get("email") || "-";
      const plan = urlParams.get("plan") || "-";
      const orderName = urlParams.get("orderName") || "-";
      const orderId = urlParams.get("orderId") || "-";
      const paymentKey = urlParams.get("paymentKey") || "-";
      const amount = urlParams.get("amount") || "0";

      // 정보 표시
      document.getElementById("email").textContent = email;
      document.getElementById("plan").textContent = plan;
      document.getElementById("orderName").textContent = orderName;
      document.getElementById("orderId").textContent = orderId;
      document.getElementById("paymentKey").textContent = paymentKey;
      document.getElementById("amount").textContent = parseInt(amount).toLocaleString() + "원";
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
